{"tid":1891454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲響歐洲住然後勁甩頭髮","createTime":"2020-02-22T00:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T03:05:56.000Z","uid":74591,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8534758fcdd3a1ec8d7851177e438b26b78bc15b","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽啊好撚慘屌<br />\n本身出世就係頭頂比較少 但整體頭髮幾多 就係頭頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響歐洲住咗幾年 屌次次洗頭甩好多 呢排頭皮好差<br />\n好乾 之後變得好快油 會痕好似額頭油脂粒 有小小粒粒<br />\n但個頭咁多頭髮，點做護膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚傷心啊屌<br />\n利申 絲 過多幾年會否變哈理王子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f394279dc4859023cf5e3f2b5d1db7457fd90a83","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:05:48.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"d67d5871384948ca1c0a3a30546bc8776b64940d","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:06:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"aefce23ad04bbd71078570b8ad3df98baf6ddc6e","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:06:32.000Z","msg":"721唔見人"},{"pid":"2afd6b59bcd34dbaa7c9b196f5122b43ca6731fd","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:06:44.000Z","msg":"831打死人"},{"pid":"030f10bf1fe06aa2f41c9dd14fd1bba95f747a64","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:06:57.000Z","msg":"101槍殺人"},{"pid":"9223080a994b6033b7f819fd16c85afb204cb0eb","tid":1891454,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T00:07:52.000Z","msg":"114阻救人"},{"pid":"51d32b157ab86266f59cc89041a9349e1d7f15b1","tid":1891454,"uid":131078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc